{"word":"G5364 - φιλανθρώπως - philanthrṓpōs - fil-an-thro'-poce - Courteously","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φιλανθρώπως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">philanthrṓpōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fil-an-thro'-poce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Courteously</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பட்சமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"humanely, kindly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from a compound of <a href=\"#/G5384 - φίλος - phílos - fee'-los/5384\">G5384</a> and <a href=\"#/G444 - ἄνθρωπος - ánthrōpos - anth'-ro-pos/444\">G444</a>; <i>fondly to man</i> (philanthropically), that is, <i>humanely:</i> - courteously.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}